<div class="container">
  <h2>Welcome to DonorTrack!</h2>
  <p>Thank you for signing up. To complete your registration, please verify your email address.</p>
  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <%= link_to "Verify My Email Address", identity_email_verification_url(sid: @signed_id), style: "background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
  </p>
  <p>If you did not create an account with DonorTrack, please disregard this email.</p>
  <p>Thank you for joining DonorTrack!<br>The DonorTrack Team</p>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@donortrack.com">contact us</a>.</p>
    <p>This email link will expire in <%= distance_of_time_in_words(Time.current, Time.current + @time_to_expire) %>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
